Package: ubuntu-download-manager-client-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: ubuntu-download-manager-common-dev(= ${binary:Version}),
         ubuntu-download-manager-client1(= ${binary:Version}),
         ${shlibs:Depends},
         ${misc:Depends}
Description: QT library for Ubuntu Download Manager - development files
 .
 This package contains the header that can be used to allow an application use the Ubuntu Download Manager client library.

